ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[According to the information received from the reference laboratory
at Onderstepoort, the current outbreak is caused by AHS virus
serotype 2. (see ref 20030318.0675).
Details on the AHS vaccine, produced and available in South Africa,
are to be seen at
<http://bigfive.jl.co.za/pdf_files/p2063.pdf>
The vaccine is presented as 2 separate injections with different AHS
virus types, the second combination to be administered at least 3
weeks after the first. - Mod.AS]
